      <p><strong>Need Flexibility:</strong> Lease (return, upgrade, or convert)
      <br><strong>Need Stability:</strong> Buying (ownership, predictable long-term costs)</p>

      <h2>The Bottom Line: Right Tool for Right Job</h2>

